	name = "update";
	default_raw_text = "Yet another frontiersman attack, we've been here for almost eight years now, and they still won't leave us alone. I'm just glad the guns seem to be holding up. Everyone's been more on edge, recently. There's been more and more traffic in the sector, I've told the town that if anyone lands, they should make get arms ready and board windows, but don't go picking a fight unless they get close. I hope level heads will see a well-armed town and stay away, but.. I just have to hope it's all enough."
